Monaco Grand Prix Halted After Petrov Crash; Sebastian Vettel Leads Race

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-05-29T13:57:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-29/monaco-grand-prix-halted-after-petrov-crash-sebastian-vettel-leads-race.html
Today’s Monaco Grand Prix was halted
six laps from the end after a crash involving Renault’s Vitaly
Petrov. The race is due to resume, with Red Bull’s Sebastian
Vettel in the lead.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  